  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/253/mode/1up">253</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/254/mode/1up">254</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, muṉṉar viṉaiyiyaluḷ viṉaiyeccam eṉṟu ōtappaṭṭaṉavaṟṟukkaṇ āvatōr ilakkaṇam uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : viṉaiyeccam eṉṟu kūṟappaṭṭaṉa ceyyuṭkaṭṭāmvantu muṭipu koṇṭataṉ ṟaṉmaippālēnillā; niṉṟāṟ poruḷicaiyāvātalāl, ōr eccantirintu ōr eccamākiyum niṟkum ilakkaṇattiṉaiyuṭaiya eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : ñāyiṟu paṭṭu vantāṉ, ñāyiṟu paṭa vantāṉ eṉpatumaṉ ākaṟpālatu.</p>
<p>paṭa eṉpatu ceyaveṉeccam ; atu tirintu paṭṭu eṉṉuñ ceyteṉeccamāki niṉṟateṉpatu.</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC456-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'kōḻikūvip pularntatu'</l></lg>
<p>eṉpatūum ceyaveṉeccañ ceyteṉeccamākit tirintu niṉṟatu eṉpatu.</p>
<p>aṅṅaṉam niṉṟavēṉum, avaṟṟaic ceyaveṉeccamāka vuṇarntukoḷal vēṇṭum, allākkāṟ coṉmuṭipu eytātu. eṉṉai, 'ñāyiṟu paṭṭu' eṉṟakkāl, vantāṉ eṉṟalum muṭiyaṟpālatu. piṉṉum ñāyiṟṟiṉmēl viṉaikoṇṭu muṭiyaṟpāṟṟu,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC456-Iḷam-cit2">
<l>'mutaṉilai mūṉṟum viṉaimutal muṭiyum'</l> <p>[tol. col. viṉai - 31]</p></lg>
<p>eṉṟu uraittārākaliṉ eṉpatu. kōḻi kūvap pularntatu eṉpataṟkum aḵtu okkum.</p>
<p>iṉi,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC456-Iḷam-cit3">
<l>'mōyiṉa ḷuyirtta kālai'</l>	<p>[akam - 5]</p></lg>
<p>eṉpuḻi, mōntu eṉṉum viṉaiyeccam, mōyiṉaḷ eṉa muṟṟuccol vāypāṭṭāṟ ṟirintu niṉṟatēṉum, viṉaiyeccamē yākalvēṇṭum. piṟavum aṉṉa.</p>
<p>piṟa eṉṟataṉāl,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC456-Iḷam-cit4">
<l>'ēri ṉuḻāa ruḻavar puyaleṉṉum</l>
<l>vāri vaḷaṅkuṉṟik kāl'</l>	<p>[kuṟaḷ. vāṉciṟappu - 4]</p></lg>
<p>eṉpatu, kuṉṟiyakkāl eṉṉum viṉaiyeccam kuṉṟikkāl eṉa niṉṟatu.	(60)</p>
 </body>
  </text>

